org.eclipse.jst.jsf.facesconfig.emf
Interface ManagedBeanType

All Known Implementing Classes:
ManagedBeanTypeImpl
public interface ManagedBeanType

A representation of the model object 'Managed Bean Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Display Name
  • Icon
  • Managed Bean Name
  • Managed Bean Class
  • Managed Bean Scope
  • Managed Property
  • Map Entries
  • List Entries
  • Managed Bean Extension
  • Id

See Also:
FacesConfigPackage.getManagedBeanType()
